      <title>达拉斯罕见降雪 地面结冰 数百架航班受灾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/rare-dallas-snow-and-ice-ground-hundreds-of-flights-across-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场冬季风暴给达拉斯带来了大雪，并给美国南部带来了冰冻和雨夹雪的威胁，导致 1,000 多架航班停飞，并增加了该地区停电的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/rare-dallas-snow-and-ice-ground-hundreds-of-flights-across-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 15:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
